name: Superciety
description: The need for belonging is still present and nowadays with the age of internet and the tools we have at our disposal, we are at a point of global identity. We are anywhere, everywhere, almost anytime. Superciety is here to deliver identity, belonging, purpose and prosperity to its followers. Superciety is a launchpad for individuals and projects using all the tools provided in Elrond’s blockchain. A place where every individual is a pool of resources and skills.
